.TH "LIGHTNING-WALLET-BALANCE-CHECK" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-wallet-balance-check \- compute ledger balance for a wallet
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning wallet-balance-check
.I wallet_name
.SH DESCRIPTION
Reads the wallet's SQLite ledger and computes the net balance by summing credits minus debits.
.PP
Output: JSON object with wallet name and balance_sat.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-wallet-info (1),
.BR lightning-wallet-history-export (1)
